title: Call of duty zombies complete soundtrack (World at War + Black O
description:
This is the most complete compilation of call of duty zombies mod songs !
It includes every single music from every single map starting from Nacht der untoten of World at War and ending with Origins of Black Ops 2. And it includes even all songs of dead ops arcade.

All 38 songs are organized with artists, title, map name, number.
